cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR. 

The paper proposes a method for generating accurate temporal action proposals from untrimmed videos, which is a task related to computer vision and machine learning. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The proposed method also involves the use of a relation-aware module, which suggests the paper may also be relevant to cs.MM (Multimedia), as well as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) due to the use of deep learning techniques. Finally, the paper evaluates its method on two benchmark datasets, indicating a potential relevance to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as well.
